    Interface Description
    LocaleProvider
    Manages the Locale restring should currently display string resources in.
    MutableStringRepository
    A mutable interface StringRepository
    StringRepository
    Immutable repository of strings resources. Restring supports all 3 types of string resources: strings, quantityStrings & stringArrays.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Restring
    A Android library to replace string resources dynamically. Restring supports all 3 types of string resources: strings, quantity strings, & string arrays.
